TP53 HIST1H3B,H3F3A,HIST1H3C alterations in cohort


format_ATRX <- merge_dna_alt_ATRX %>%
  left_join(merged_rna_ATRX,suffix=c("_DNA","_RNA"),by=c("Kids_First_Participant_ID","sample_id","cell_line_composition")) %>%
  dplyr::select("Kids_First_Participant_ID","Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID_DNA","Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID_RNA",everything()) %>%
  dplyr::select(-Hugo_Symbol) %>% 
  dplyr::mutate("alterations_ATRX"=case_when(
    !is.na(ATRX_MOD_HIGH_mut_consensus) | !is.na(ATRX_loss_consensus) ~ "ATRX_loss",
           !is.na(ATRX_gain_consensus)  ~ "ATRX_gain",
    TRUE ~ NA_character_
  ))
  


format_DAXX <- merge_dna_alt_DAXX %>%
  left_join(merged_rna_DAXX,suffix=c("_DNA","_RNA"),by=c("Kids_First_Participant_ID","sample_id","cell_line_composition")) %>%
  dplyr::select("Kids_First_Participant_ID","Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID_DNA","Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID_RNA",everything()) %>%
  dplyr::select(-Hugo_Symbol)  %>% 
  dplyr::mutate("alterations_DAXX"=case_when(
      !is.na(DAXX_loss_consensus) ~ "DAXX_loss",
       !is.na(DAXX_gain_consensus) ~ "DAXX_gain",
      TRUE ~ NA_character_
  ))


format_TERT <- merge_dna_alt_TERT %>%
  left_join(merged_rna_TERT,suffix=c("_DNA","_RNA"),by=c("Kids_First_Participant_ID","sample_id","cell_line_composition")) %>% 
  dplyr::select("Kids_First_Participant_ID","Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID_DNA","Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID_RNA",everything()) %>%
  dplyr::select(-Hugo_Symbol) %>% 
  dplyr::mutate("alterations_TERT"=case_when(
    !is.na(TERT_MOD_HIGH_mut_consensus) | !is.na(TERT_upstream_mut_consensus) |
      !is.na(TERT_amplification_consensus) | !is.na(TERT_gain_consensus) |
      !is.na(TERT_loss_consensus) ~ "TERT_mod",
    TRUE ~ NA_character_
  ))
  

all_alterations <- full_join(format_ATRX,
                             format_DAXX,
                             by=c("Kids_First_Participant_ID",
                                  "Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID_DNA",
                                  "Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID_RNA",
                                  "cell_line_composition",
                                  "sample_id")) %>%
  full_join(format_TERT,by=c("Kids_First_Participant_ID",
                             "Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID_DNA",
                             "Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID_RNA",
                             "cell_line_composition",
                             "sample_id")) %>%
  # since there are NA in RNA Ids in some rows 
  # using DNA which is non NA to match to histology
  full_join(cohort_plot_labels[which(cohort_plot_labels$experimental_strategy != "RNA-Seq" & cohort_plot_labels$composition == "Solid Tissue"),],
            by=c("Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID_DNA"="Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID",
            "Kids_First_Participant_ID","sample_id","parent_aliquot_id"))

all_alterations[all_alterations == 0] <- NA

all_alterations <- all_alterations %>% 
  dplyr::mutate("defining_alt" = 
                  case_when(
                    !is.na(alterations_TERT) &
                      !is.na(alterations_DAXX) & 
                      !is.na(alterations_ATRX) ~ paste(alterations_TERT,alterations_DAXX,alterations_ATRX),
                !is.na(alterations_DAXX) & 
                  !is.na(alterations_ATRX) ~ paste(alterations_DAXX,alterations_ATRX),
                !is.na(alterations_TERT) & 
                  !is.na(alterations_ATRX) ~ paste(alterations_TERT,alterations_ATRX),
                !is.na(alterations_TERT) & 
                  !is.na(alterations_DAXX) ~ paste(alterations_TERT,alterations_DAXX),
                !is.na(alterations_ATRX) ~ alterations_ATRX,
                !is.na(alterations_DAXX) ~ alterations_DAXX,
                !is.na(alterations_TERT) ~ alterations_TERT,
                TRUE ~ "no SNV/CNV alt"
                )
  )
all_alterations_ratio <- all_alterations %>%
  left_join(telomere_ratio,by = c("Kids_First_Participant_ID",
                                "Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID_DNA" = "Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID_tumor")) %>%
  dplyr::select("Kids_First_Participant_ID","Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID_DNA",
                "Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID_RNA","sample_id", ends_with("fpkm"),ends_with("fusion"),ends_with("consensus"),ends_with("manta"),"ratio","defining_alt" ,"broad_histology") %>%
  dplyr::mutate(ratio = log2(ratio)) %>%
  left_join(terra,by = c("Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID_RNA" = "SampleID")) %>%
  left_join(ccircle[,c("CCA.Dot.Blot","Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID")],by = c("Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID_DNA" = "Kids_First_Biospecimen_ID")) %>%
  write_tsv(file.path("../output/all_alterations_ATRX_DAXX_TERT.tsv"))
